                        h2(id="layout") Layout
                        h3(id="layout-grid") Grid
                        p The airframe grid system consists of 12 columns. The variables that dictate the grid width and column spacing can be found in <code class="docs--code-inline">assets/layout.css</code>.
                        h4 Configuration Variables
