                        h4 Responsive utilities
                        p Grid classes can be modified at various breakpoints using responsive utility classes. The breakpoints are set in <code class="docs--code-inline">assets/layout.css</code>.
                        p
                            table
                                thead
                                    tr
                                        th Variable
                                        th Description
                                        th Default
                                tbody
                                    tr
                                        td <code class="docs--code-inline">--mq-l</code>
                                        td Media query for large screens
                                        td <code class="docs--code-inline">width > 1024px</code>
                                    tr
                                        td <code class="docs--code-inline">--mq-m</code>
                                        td Media query for medium screens
                                        td <code class="docs--code-inline">width <= 1024px</code>
                                    tr
                                        td <code class="docs--code-inline">--mq-s</code>
                                        td Media query for small screens
                                        td <code class="docs--code-inline">width <= 768px</code>
                        p Responsive utilities can be used instead of declaring a default column size, or in addition to a default column size; this allows you to create mobile-first or desktop-first layouts.
