                        h2(id="tables") Tables
                        p Tables are styled with the fewest elements possible. For more styling, including text alignment and color, use Utility classes. For guidelines on how to style tables, read <a href="https://medium.com/mission-log/design-better-data-tables-430a30a00d8c#.od49lsyoa">Design Better Data Tables</a>.
